# Working with terraform inazure
#providers
#resources
This project demonstrates how to use Terraform to create and manage an Azure Resource Group using the HashiCorp AzureRM provider.
It includes configuration files for initializing Terraform, authenticating with Azure, and defining the desired infrastructure state.

